# 📊 Netflix Excel Dashboard Project

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is an interactive Excel dashboard created to analyze Netflix dataset. It focuses on extracting meaningful insights from raw data using data cleaning, transformation, and visualization techniques.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Analyze Netflix movies and TV shows data
* Identify trends in content type, genre, and release year
* Build an interactive dashboard for better visualization

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies Used

* Microsoft Excel
* Pivot Tables
* Charts & Graphs
* Slicers & Filters

---

## 📂 Dataset Details

The dataset includes:

* Title
* Type (Movie/TV Show)
* Genre
* Release Year
* Ratings

---

## ⚙️ Process

1. Data Cleaning (handling missing values, formatting)
2. Data Transformation
3. Creating Pivot Tables
4. Building Charts
5. Designing Interactive Dashboard

---

## 📈 Key Insights

* Distribution of Movies vs TV Shows
* Most common genres
* Trends over release years
* Content rating analysis

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features

* Interactive slicers
* Dynamic charts
* Easy-to-understand visuals

---

## 🚀 Conclusion

This project demonstrates the ability to clean, analyze, and visualize data using Excel. It helps in making data-driven decisions through interactive dashboards.

